---
title: "Basic Verification"
---

This section will describe basic verification methodologies used by the Syrian Archive

Similar to the archival and collection methodology, the initial verification methodology is also broken into five distinct steps
- [Aggregate metadata from visual evidence](en/topics/2-basic-verification/2-step-1);
- [Verify the source of the video](en/topics/2-basic-verification/2-step-2);
- [Verify the location of the video](en/topics/2-basic-verification/2-step-3);
- [Verify the dates in which the video was filmed and uploaded](en/topics/2-basic-verification/2-step-4), and;
- [Publish verified video evidence on the Syrian Archiveâ€™s online database](en/topics/2-basic-verification/2-step-5 
